data.description: Large corner lot with no back neighbors!! SPACIOUS, BRAND-NEW HOME WITH 5 BEDROOMS AND A GAME ROOM! This gorgeous two-story home at Pinewood Trails offers a true retreat for the whole family, showcasing an expansive family room downstairs and a spacious game room upstairs. The modern, upgraded kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, abundant cabinet storage, and a full set of Whirlpool brand appliances including a refrigerator and a built-in microwave. The private, downstairs master suite includes a separate garden tub, step-in shower and a huge walk-in closet. Enjoy an amazing amount of space upstairs, where four spacious bedrooms each feature a walk-in closet, and the second full bathroom includes a separate vanity area and storage. Residents at Pinewood Trails will appreciate the wooded, peaceful surroundings, a private neighborhood park, and easy access to US-59 and TX-105.
